Description:
This repository contains a simple login page implementation with a captcha feature, designed for web applications. The login page is built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and it incorporates a captcha system to enhance security and prevent automated attacks. Users can enter their username, solve a captcha challenge, and then proceed to log in.

Key Features:

Clean and responsive design for a user-friendly experience.
Captcha system to protect against automated login attempts.
Utilizes Font Awesome for a visually appealing refresh icon.
SweetAlert2 integration for enhanced alert messages.
Easily customizable for integration into various web projects.
How to Use:

Clone the repository to your local machine.
Open the index.html file in a web browser.
Enter a username, solve the captcha, and click the login button.
Experience the login process with captcha validation.
